[+++ b/website/index.html, +            <h4>Header Manipulation</h4>, +            <p>A request Header can be updated dynamically using the <code>@Header</code> annotation. A corresponding String parameter must be provided to the <code>@Header</code>. If the value is null, the header will be omitted.</p>, +            <pre class="prettyprint">@GET("/user"), +void getUser(@Header("Authorization") String authorization, Callback&lt;User> callback)</pre>, +            <p>You can set static headers for a method using the <code>@Headers</code> annotation.</p>, +            <pre class="prettyprint">@Headers("Cache-Control: max-age=640000"), +@GET("/widget/list"), +List&lt;Widget> widgetList();</pre>, +            <pre class="prettyprint">@Headers({, +    "Accept: application/vnd.github.v3.full+json",, +    "User-Agent: Octodroid-App", +}), +@GET("/users/{username}"), +User getUser(@Path("username") String username);</pre>, +            <p>Note that headers do not overwrite each other. All headers with the same name will be included in the request.</p>, +]